---
import PageLayout from '@layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="About · Akshay Bajpai"
  description="From medical AI research to building products people use daily. Architect of systems, builder of intelligence."
>
  <article class="about-page section-surface">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <header class="about-header" data-reveal>
        <h1 class="about-title">About</h1>
        <p class="about-lead">Architect of systems. Builder of intelligence.</p>
      </header>
      <div class="about-prose" data-reveal-stagger>
        <p>
          I operate at the intersection of AI infrastructure, systems thinking, and product. My work spans
          research, architecture, and shipping—each system designed with explicit tradeoffs and long-term
          maintainability in mind.
        </p>
        <p>
          I hold a Master's with distinction in Artificial Intelligence & Intelligent Systems. I have
          published research and shipped products that people use daily. I prefer building with minimal
          dependencies, clear architecture, and performance as a non-negotiable.
        </p>
        <p>
          This site is a thinking laboratory: essays, case studies, and technical writing that reflect how
          I approach problems. No fluff, no placeholders. If you want to collaborate on AI systems,
          architecture, or performance-critical products, <a href="/contact" class="link-hover">get in touch</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: var(--space-32) var(--space-8);
    position: relative;
  }
  .about-inner {
    max-width: var(--content-narrow);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-20);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-8);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: border-color var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .about-header.reveal-visible {
    border-color: var(--color-border-strong);
  }
  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .about-lead {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .about-prose {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }
  .about-prose p {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-8);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    transition: opacity var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-out-expo), transform var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .about-prose a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    transition: color var(--duration-fast);
  }
  .about-prose a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
